column36: Made a good start to her chasing career and she's a very solid contender under a penalty
column37: Made all on chase debut at Kempton (2m2f, good) in October and again ran well when fourth of seven at Newbury (2m, good to soft) last time; those were in handicaps against males and she's a very solid contender today under a penalty; effective on soft ground over hurdles.
